last_episode_to_air.name: The Most You You Can Be
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Miss American Lady pageant declares its winner as shocking truths come to light, and Patty embraces her inner self, much to Bob's dismay.

name: Insatiable
overview: A bullied teenager turns to beauty pageants as a way to exact her revenge, with the help of a disgraced coach who soon realizes he's in over his head.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Bullied teenager Patty goes to court to defend her fight with a homeless man. Defense attorney Bob sees a chance to redeem himself by helping her.

episodes.name: Skinny Is Magic
episodes.overview: After a suspicious fire at a motel, Patty wonders whether she was at fault. She and Nonnie try to solve the mystery on the first day of senior year.

episodes.name: Miss Bareback Buckaroo
episodes.overview: Bob takes Patty to a pageant in Alabama to meet his former mentor, Stella Rose. Coralee gets an unwelcome visit from her sister.

episodes.name: WMBS
episodes.overview: Patty contemplates what to do with Stella Rose's necklace while also striving to win her first pageant, a mother-daughter event.

episodes.name: Bikinis and Bitches
episodes.overview: Someone hacks Patty's phone and frames her for cyberbullying. Magnolia has an idea on how to save the day. Brick has a heart-to-heart with his dad.

episodes.name: Dunk 'N' Donut
episodes.overview: Nonnie comes to terms with what she wants. Meanwhile, Patty struggles to decide between two love interests and prepares for her baptism.

episodes.name: Miss Magic Jesus
episodes.overview: The ladies get ready for the Miss Magic Jesus pageant and the last-minute Bible trivia quiz. Bob wonders about his connection to Roxy.

episodes.name: Wieners and Losers
episodes.overview: Patty has a very important decision to make about her future. Bob's father tells him to save his marriage with Coralee.

episodes.name: Bad Kitty
episodes.overview: Pastor Mike convinces Patty she has a demon inside of her and Christian offers up a suggestion. Bob grapples with his feelings.

episodes.name: Banana Heart Banana
episodes.overview: Bob Barnard leans in to his truth. Patty plans a charity roast in order to raise money for Dixie. Coralee comes up with a business idea.

episodes.name: Winners Win. Period.
episodes.overview: Patty tries to make amends. The Bobs struggle with how to move forward. Regina believes in Coralee's entrepreneurial plan.

episodes.name: Why Bad Things Happen
episodes.overview: Nonnie and Brick search for Patty when she goes missing. Bob is faced with a seemingly impossible decision. Regina gives Christian advice.

episodes.name: Pig
episodes.overview: Patty and Bob work frantically to cover up her crimes and are met with a few surprises. The regionals queen is given her crown.

episodes.name: Dead Girl
episodes.overview: While the police investigate the recent murder, Patty works to unite the pageant contestants in a public relations attempt to change the headlines.

episodes.name: Boomerang
episodes.overview: Patty finds an eating disorder sponsor and meets a significant person. Bob takes on a new client. Coralee encourages Bob Barnard to run for mayor.

episodes.name: Poison Patty
episodes.overview: Coralee and Regina throw a feminist period party. Bob goes polyamorous speed dating. Patty is haunted by visions while mentoring a "little sister."

episodes.name: Finding Magnolia
episodes.overview: Magnolia visits Hughes University to try to piece together her lost memories. Dixie learns a shocking secret. Bob launches his mayoral campaign.

episodes.name: Eat and Run
episodes.overview: A crushed Patty throws herself into her newfound talent with the help of a tempting instructor. Brick decides he wants to be a social media influencer.

episodes.name: Full Brazilian
episodes.overview: Nonnie investigates a crime. Patty competes in the state pageant while simultaneously working her recovery program. Angie encounters trouble.

episodes.name: Pretty in Prison
episodes.overview: A tragedy lands Patty in prison, where she helps plan a pageant. Meanwhile, Coralee and Bob's division of their home results in a surprise.

episodes.name: Ladybomb
episodes.overview: The Bobs face off in a heated debate with quite a few twists, while Coralee tries to remove herself from danger. Patty and Nonnie go on a ghost tour.

episodes.name: The Most You You Can Be
episodes.overview: The Miss American Lady pageant declares its winner as shocking truths come to light, and Patty embraces her inner self, much to Bob's dismay.
